description:
Dorion is an alternative Discord client aimed towards lower-spec or storage-sensitive PCs that supports themes, plugins, and more!


Changes
- Add --proxy-url CLI option
- Add --legacy-fetch CLI option (Windows-only)
  - This can help with issues where CSS or plugins fail to load
- Add --help CLI option
- Change how early the CSP extension loads (Windows only)
- Change shelter plugins domain (#345)
